task.summary: voting working really well now with account/session storage. About to add voting buttons to the app list view.
Cleaning up for release, nearly there!
MainActivity listview now gets updated by reddinator if a user votes. Enhanced login/auth system. Added loading bar for ViewRedditActivity voting. Various other fixes
MainActivity listview now gets updated by reddinator if a user votes. Enhanced login/auth system. Added loading bar for ViewRedditActivity voting. Various other fixes
fixed a few bugs, created signed apk, commencing final tests for 2.0 release YAY!
fixed manifest version number, created new apk
Fix of NPE, account deletion, again. this should hopefully be final version 2.0
Start of version 2.1. Add front page and all to subreddit list after import. Added thumbnail caching to widget. Started account webview.

Added actionbar back buttons to all views. Added open in browser option to reddinator view. Modified share menu option to match; enables picking which link to share. Fixed Actionbar theme issue and tweaked menu bar. Various UI tweaks.
Changed voting system so that they are persistent on the widget. Added immersive mode to fullscreen video. Added transparent widget theme.
Fixed subreddit import problem. tweaked layout
Fixed cookie problem. Most definitly final 2.1
enhanced default images added nsfw flag
Added set subreddit feature to all subreddits list
Added old auth flush, fixed app feed image view showing old image when loading
fixed html comments rendering & listview load view
Added load more comments. Slow as it's loading comments one by one rather than using reddit's unbelievably fucked morechildren endpoint.
added more fontawesome icons and comments sorting/reload.
added delete and most of edit comment functions
completed comment editing. replaced frament activity with view pager. added new actionbar icons. Added mail check items to prefs activity.
finished mail check fixed styling issues. added both urls to to share option. added share and open menu to web view.
updated manifest, feature freeze for v2.3.
+ mark read "feature" to inbox. + item displays subreddit when on Front Page or all
